videos.headline: Aggies' Alaka catches interception off weird ricochet
videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Fitzgerald throws a pass intended for Jordan Thomas, and Texas A&M's Otaro Alaka catches the ball of the deflection for no gain.

videos.headline: QB Fitzgerald puts the Bulldogs on the board first
videos.description: Mississippi State quarterback Nick Fitzgerald runs the ball up the middle, pulling a defender into the end zone with him for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Bulldogs' Williams goes airborne
videos.description: Bulldogs' Aeris Williams goes airborne after trying to hurdle over multiple Texas A&M defenders.

videos.headline: Bulldogs QB Fitzgerald runs for 45 yards
videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Fitzgerald finds a gap and runs the ball 45 yards.

videos.headline: Bulldogs' Fitzgerald makes nice throw for TD
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald makes great throw to Donald Gray for another Mississippi State touchdown.

videos.headline: Mullen discusses the challenges in first half
videos.description: Mississippi State's head coach Dan Mullen breaks down all the challenges the team has faced in the first half despite leading.

videos.headline: Bulldogs' Fitzgerald makes great throw to Green
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald makes a great throw to Farrod Green for 41 yards for a Bulldogs' first down.

videos.headline: Thomas wide open in end zone for Bulldogs' TD
videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Fitzgerald finds Jordan Thomas wide open in the end zone for another Bulldogs touchdown.

videos.headline: Mond's big run puts Aggies in red zone
videos.description: Texas A&M's Kellen Mond with a fake pass option, and he runs for 33 yards putting the Aggies in scoring position.

videos.headline: Ford with Texas A&M's first TD
videos.description: Aggies run the Wildcat option and snap it to Keith Ford, who pushes through the defense for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Aggies' Mond throws another interception
videos.description: Kellen Mond's pass is tipped around until Bulldogs' Lashard Durr snags the ball and returns it for 20 yards.

videos.headline: Gibson TD extends Mississippi State's lead
videos.description: Bulldogs' Nick Gibson receives the hand off, plows through the defense and reaches out for his first career touchdown.

videos.headline: Referee completely ignores Mullen's call for timeout
videos.description: Dan Mullen tries to call for a time out right in front of the referee who completely ignores him. Eventually Mullen is granted a timeout but still is not happy.

videos.headline: Peters goes 90 yards to the house for a pick-six
videos.description: Nick Starkel's pass is picked off by the Bulldogs' Jamal Peters who returns it for a 90-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Buckley takes defender on a ride for 70-yard TD
videos.description: Camron Buckley can't be denied as he runs nearly 20 yards with a defender on his back for a 70-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Mullen: 'Our guys played to our standard'
videos.description: Mississippi State coach Dan Mullen talks about the Bulldogs' 35-14 win over Texas A&M and what it means moving forward.

videos.headline: Fitzgerald leads Bulldogs to victory over Aggies
videos.description: ESPN's Rod Gilmore and Mark Jones break down Nick Fitzgerald's performance, and say he was firing from all cylinders.
